## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
We will verify API status using simple HTTP scripts or direct Node script tests.
- Verify JWT login and role locking (e.g., job seeker login cannot access recruiter routes).
- Verify AI matching engine score calculation and automatic forwarding (>85% matching).

### Manual Verification
We will run the development servers and use a web browser to test:
1. Opening the app and viewing the Landing Page.
2. Clicking "Get Started" to see the "Job Seeker" vs. "Recruiter" Welcome Page.
3. Registering a student account (e.g., `student@test.com`) and verifying that logging in as Recruiter fails with a clear message.
4. Filling the Student Profile, adding projects/skills, generating the resume, and viewing AI scores.
5. Logging in as Recruiter, posting a job with specific skill/CGPA filters, and verifying the AI matching rank.
6. Verifying the auto-forwarding feature (profiles >= 85% match are instantly forwarded to the recruiter applicant list).
7. Verifying the Admin dashboard functionality (managing and flagging).
